 Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe whose last words are 'there is no God but Allah,' will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3116 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0630\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062c\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42236,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/09\/20\/reward-blinded\/","url_meta":{"origin":40019,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Eyesight: Reward for believers when blinded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty says: Whoever has his two dear eyes taken away by Me and he patiently awaits his compensation, I am not pleased to reward him with anything except Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2401 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":786,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/16\/sabr-mawt-leads-to-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":40019,"posit